		<td><b>Dr. Mario stage clear music cuts out</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In Dr. Mario, after you clear a stage, it prompts the player to press START to advance to the next level (&quot;STAGE CLEAR | TRY NEXT&quot;).  On that screen, it plays music that cuts out with a strange chirp after about about 10 seconds.  Is that a bug in Dr. Mario?  And, if so, is there any way to listen to the full song?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


